data.description: The Chadwick Plan built by Stephen Elliott Homes. Beautiful 4BR 2.5 Baths. Home is a must see and like new! Features include Hardwood floors in foyer, 42" cabinets, Granite Countertops in Kitchen, tile backsplash and trey or vaulted ceilings. Fireplace in the family room along with spacious master bedroom with sitting area. Great location! The community features a swimming pool and tennis courts! 10 minutes from the airport and 20 minutes to downtown!
